PR statistics have made the previous recordings of their 2 day
Introduction to Statistics Using R and Rstudio FREE. The reason behind this
is nearly all of our courses require some prior knowledge and experience
with R and statistics.

https://www.prstatistics.com/course/introduction-to-statistics-using-r-and-rstudio-irrs03r/

